{"tid":1102803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"流浮山男子遭鎚仔扑頭搶銀包 血流披臉送院","createTime":"2019-04-12T03:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T03:33:31.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cee884551fc00c7682ea223a75ce2578d50fae00","tid":1102803,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T03:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6bSqkkE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6bSqkkE.png&h=f79df569&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HhAjpNk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHhAjpNk.png&h=7a1688f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主報稱在公廁附近被搶銀包，警員到場調查。張家豪攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YOHUX7k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYOHUX7k.png&h=6917aba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主負傷返家報警。張家豪攝<br />\n<br />\n流浮山民德路鰲磡村公廁對開，早上9時16分，一名45歲男子被人用鎚仔扑頭，搶去他後褲袋的銀包，賊人得手後逃去。事主頭部受傷，血流披臉，負傷返家報警求助，他清醒送往天水圍醫院治理，警方正通緝一名年約30歲男賊人。"}]}